{
  "text": "Serological studies have shown a worldwide distribution of BDV in sheep and goat. A BD-like syndrome in goats has been reported in southern part of Korea since 1998. In a retrospective study, BVDV-2 in native goat was identified and characterized in 2005 [CITATION_1] . BDV have not been identified in Korean goats until now.",
